---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout lang="en" title="About" description="The filmmakers behind First Up Weddings: a cinematic eye, a sense for emotion, and quiet presence on your wedding day.">

  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-cream pt-32">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">

        <!-- Portrait -->
        <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-[201px]">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-brand-warm overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/portrait.jpg" alt="Adem Kocyigit of First Up Weddings, on a wedding day with camera and gimbal" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Text -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading text-brand-dark mb-8">The people behind the camera.</h1>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Filmmakers, storytellers, and the people who stay quietly in the background on your wedding day. That is First Up Weddings.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our passion for storytelling brought us to film. Short films, directing, visual storytelling — that is how we learned to express emotion in images, not just show them. And exactly that is what we bring to your wedding.
            </p>
            <p>
              What fascinates us about wedding films: no other day in life is so full of real, unplanned, beautiful moments. The trembling at the altar. The look right before you see each other for the first time. The laughter of your friends. The tears of your parents. These moments happen only once, and we are there to preserve them.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-10 p-8 bg-brand-warm">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-brand-dark mb-4">Our promise to you:</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
              We stage nothing. We interrupt nothing. We are simply there: attentive, quiet, and with a sense for the moments that define your day. The result is a film that doesn't feel like a video, but like a memory.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-10">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-brand-dark mb-4">What defines us as filmmakers:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-brand-text">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> A cinematic eye, shaped by directing and short-film work</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> A sense for rhythm, emotion, and atmosphere</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Experience in professional video production</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Genuine excitement for your story</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <blockquote class="mt-10 text-xl font-heading italic text-brand-accent">
            &ldquo;A great wedding film doesn't show what happened. It lets you feel how it felt.&rdquo;
          </blockquote>

          <div class="mt-10">
            <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-primary">Get to know us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
